     The question in my mind still is how much is slight.
    </p>
    <p>
     I need to put the things thru their paces in the other direction to get a good answer.
    </p>
    <p>
     Right now I'm looking at little circles on paper with lines of travel running thru them and mumbling a lot.
    </p>
    <p>
